CARD 20

Which emergency equipment is essential for remote area seed collection?

A) Satellite phone or EPIRB
B) Compression bandages for snake bite
C) First aid kit
D) All of the above

<details>
<summary>✅ Answer</summary>
**D) All of the above** – Remote area collections require comprehensive safety equipment: communication device, first aid with snake bandages, and emergency evacuation plan.
</details>

